# -*-cperl-*-

=head1 NAME

REDUCE_FTS_SCAN - Recipe for processing FTS-2 SCAN data

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This is a basic recipe for processing FTS-2 SCAN data. All processing is done in
the _FTS2_DR_ primitive.

=head1 NOTES

None.

=head1 DISPLAY

None.

